import { Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown, NavDropdownProps, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
const Navigation = () => {
    return (
        <Navbar collapsOnSelect fized='top' expands='lg' bg="dark" variant='dark'>
            <Container>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls='responsive-navbar-nav' />
                <Navbar.Collapse id='responsive-navbar-nav'>
                    <NavDropdown>
                        <NavDropdown.Link href='/Portal'>Home</NavDropdown.Link>
                        <NavDropdown.Link href='/App'>Testing</NavDropdown.Link>
                    </NavDropdown>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
    );
}

export default Navigation
